Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93698,95867}{\i1}Meimi Haneoka is 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:39.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95867,99871}{\i1}By day she is a happy student\Nat St. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100079,103249}{\i1}But at night, she becomes\Nthe phantom thief St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:47.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103249,107962}{\i1}to do good deeds for all who come\Nasking for help from Seira, a nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:52.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107962,112216}{\i1}Looking to capture the elusive St. Tail\Nis an amateur detective
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112216,114218}{\i1}and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115094,119766}{\i1}As for Meimi, she may have more than\Na bit of interest in such a determined boy.
Comment: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:01.14,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:121142,121142}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.48,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:123019,125480}Meimi's lover is a hedgehog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:14.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133863,134864}That mom of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:18.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134864,138034}It's Sunday, and she has to make me\Ngo do the grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153966,155802}Hey, hold it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170858,172694}What is it?! What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174529,177073}You're a really rude creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:57.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177073,177824}Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191462,193339}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198469,200346}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:29.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205893,209814}If it's the cat, it went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209814,210815}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212024,214110}Oh, please watch the shop\Nfor a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214402,216112}What? Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216112,217321}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220283,221200}Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234297,236007}What could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239677,240511}Y… You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241387,243347}You're the rude one\NI met the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245183,246476}Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256944,257945}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259489,261908}You're all alone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265369,267830}Cheer up, cute little hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273503,277256}You're the only person that this\Nhedgehog has warmed up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278299,279759}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282428,284263}My name is Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284263,287725}I'll come to see you ever day from\Nnow on! So let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288100,289519}So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291062,293731}Oh, no! I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293731,295650}Oh, no! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295650,296818}Hey, hold it!\NCome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296818,298653}Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302657,304867}Meimi, want to stop for\Nice cream on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:08.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304867,308538}There's a new shop that just opened\Nbeside the park on 2nd Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309038,311499}Sorry, I've got something\Nto do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311499,312875}Something to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312875,314335}A date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314544,315753}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315753,318089}Yup! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322218,323553}A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324262,325429}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327890,329475}Have you had a nice day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332019,334981}Hi! Back again?\NYou're fond of her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334981,336440}She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:42.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337149,342405}Why don't you ask your mother and\Nfather if you can buy her as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342405,345908}I promise I won't sell her to anyone\Nelse until you get their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:46.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345908,346909}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346909,349120}You won't sell her\Nto anyone else until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349829,351622}Sure. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352248,354000}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354000,355835}Wait for me, my little hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358045,359088}Mister, I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359088,360798}All right, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364468,365595}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365595,366679}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367305,370224}This hedgehog, sell him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371601,373185}But it's already…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375229,378149}Look, I said I want this hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:26.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382111,386198}Please Dad, can I?\NCan I have the hedgehog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387617,389076}Did you say hedgehog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389660,392538}That's right.\NI even have a name for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393164,394540}I'll call her Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395124,396042}Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396500,399962}The ring that dad bought you\Nis a ruby, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399962,401714}Yes, my engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401714,403507}That's why I named her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408054,410139}Hmm… a ruby…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414101,417438}It does bring back memories\Nof the old days, doesn't it, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418147,420066}It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420858,423402}Eimi, you haven't changed\Na bit since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424153,425905}Why, dear, you haven't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427073,428282}Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428866,430409}Genichiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431369,433371}Hello, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434246,435873}Oh, gee, Meimi, were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436332,439168}Of course, where else would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439168,442296}Then it's all right for me to have\Na hedgehog named Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442296,443381}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444131,445383}Phew…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446425,448803}It helps, having easy-going parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452723,453891}Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454225,455267}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456185,457895}I'm really sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458437,460815}You promised you wouldn't sell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460815,464360}He insisted on buying it.\NHe wouldn't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466737,467947}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479125,481544}Moping will get me nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:05.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481544,485506}I'm sure Ruby is having\Na nice life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485506,487216}Right! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493097,494724}"Polar Tear?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495266,497518}Yes, it's a beautiful diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:21.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497518,501272}Legend says it's a teardrop\Nof the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:26.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501564,506902}I shared the diamond with Hayase,\Nan old friend from my school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:32.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506902,512241}We took turns, keeping the gem\Nfor two months at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512658,515703}That was our agreement.\NI never expected he would betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516162,517705}He betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518289,519498}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:43.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519498,523919}Yesterday was the day I was to receive\Nthe diamond for the next two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:50.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525296,530217}Hayase, what are you saying?\NYou haven't given the diamond to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:55.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530217,535181}That's ridiculous, Kamimura.\NOf course I gave you the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537349,540561}If you doubt me, search the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543647,546025}Kamimura… maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:11.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547401,551489}You're not trying to keep the\Ndiamond all to yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:12.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552073,552990}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553699,555409}That's what you're trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555826,557203}Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557203,559955}Do you have any proof that\NI didn't give you the diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573969,576388}That's the story I heard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576889,579767}They finally called the police\Nand searched the house, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579767,581936}They couldn't find the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:48.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582770,588067}And according to the contract,\Nif the Polar Tear is lost
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:51.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588067,591362}the one that loses the gem\Nhas to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591695,592863}Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594406,596617}On top of stealing the diamond,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596617,602331}Hayase is holding him\Nliable for the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602748,604583}I'm really angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:08.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604583,608796}Phantom St. Tail\Nshall retrieve that diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:14.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609839,614760}Is something wrong?\NYou're not usually this touchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616011,617555}Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617555,619473}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619473,621350}I went to the pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621350,623227}The pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623227,626647}Someone bought my hedgehog!\NShe's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626647,630901}I'd even thought up some hedgehog\Nmagic to use on the next caper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630901,632653}What's that supposed to be?
Comment: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:32.65,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:632653,632653}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:38.65,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:638659,638659}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:43.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:643664,643664}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658762,661265}Well then, let us continue\Nfrom line 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665853,667771}Mr. Asuka! Read!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678032,679200}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681285,683162}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:28.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683162,688626}"Tonight, I'll be at the Hayase\Nmansion to get the Polar Tear"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688626,691128}"Signed, St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701138,704058}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704475,706560}That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708187,709063}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715527,719031}My Lord, forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723953,725037}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727498,728707}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730751,731919}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748269,751855}May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752982,754566}Meimi, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755401,756193}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756944,759321}To help me forget\Nmy little hedgehog…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759321,761198}I'm gonna nail this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763492,765494}I don't need your security!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765995,769957}The police checked it out, but\Nthe Polar Tear is not in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770499,772501}Whatever St. Tail\Nis supposed to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772501,774837}how can she steal something\Nthat isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:13:00.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774837,780009}But St. Tail sent me a warning\Nthat she'll show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:05.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784638,785389}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785973,788475}The Mayor's special\Nbadge of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788475,790853}I'm staking out\Nyour home, Mr. Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798819,803782}The question is\Nwhere's the diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805242,806702}That must be Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812791,813667}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814418,817629}But why is my hedgehog Ruby here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819173,822176}I must say, this is ingenious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:46.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822176,826555}No one would ever think that the\NPolar Tear is inside your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827514,830517}What a terrible thing to do!\NAbsolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832519,833979}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834813,835856}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835856,838067}It's rude of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838067,841487}but are you really sure\Nthe Polar Tear is not in the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842696,844031}Persistent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844031,846450}I told you, I handed the diamond\Nover to Kamimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848869,850120}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850120,853248}A hedgehog?\NWhat an unusual pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853248,855376}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860839,861924}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861924,863050}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871392,872684}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879650,881193}Darn, you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882361,884363}My Polar Tear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887199,888367}Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888367,889368}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891912,893747}They sure are persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898794,899795}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905968,907970}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910431,913350}What the…\NWhy are you on my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914143,915936}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918355,919898}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920441,922109}What are you chasing me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922109,923902}Shut up! Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927072,929658}Asuka Jr.! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932077,933287}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:36.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933287,936498}You brat!\NWhy are you running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936498,939126}I'm not running away,\NI'm chasing St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947426,949052}Where are you? St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949052,950554}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952431,954558}Hand over that hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:59.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954933,959021}You just wait right there!\NI'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961148,962483}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962691,964359}How hopeless can he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974786,975537}There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:22.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978457,982085}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003148,1004900}You little pest! Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006944,1009321}Hold that elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009321,1011323}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018413,1020207}It's no use trying to escape like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020207,1023126}I'll catch up to you\Nin the other elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024878,1025546}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025546,1026296}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027965,1030259}What are you planning\Nto do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030259,1033762}Shut up! The hedgehog is all…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:27.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042771,1047276}Look this way, St. Tail.\NMaybe I can see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047276,1048777}I just want to get a look at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048777,1050237}Show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050654,1051321}How…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:31.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051321,1051989}is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051989,1054241}this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:41.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057995,1061331}I'll be getting off here. Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062666,1064543}Hey! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064543,1066295}Do something, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066295,1068672}Shut up! Stop being a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:53.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068672,1073135}Too bad that elevator doesn't stop\Nuntil it gets to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:02.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079099,1082436}Wait right there!\NI'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083478,1086523}I know I should probably\Njust escape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087733,1089067}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:16.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091737,1096033}It really bugs me.\NWhy can't I just let that guy be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101288,1103540}Wait, it's coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:28.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103874,1108003}What a stupid phantom,\Nshe's going to follow us up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110464,1111590}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114092,1115886}St. Tail, we've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115886,1117596}Hand over my hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123101,1124394}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:50.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127105,1130442}I didn't think I'd get a chance\Nto use my hedgehog magic so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131151,1132444}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133362,1135447}One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135697,1137449}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152881,1155050}Oh, you were able to cough it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155050,1156843}I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:21.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157803,1161306}That's what you get for being bad\Nand hoarding the gem all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162182,1163809}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167020,1168105}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171066,1172275}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174611,1175987}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175987,1177322}Take care of the rest for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181243,1182077}A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192671,1194881}Oh, it's the Polar Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194881,1195549}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195549,1198093}Why did she give this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198093,1200011}Hey, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200679,1201471}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201471,1203724}Hayase is out cold down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:07.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203724,1207477}But I'm arresting him\Non charges of fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:11.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208061,1211648}And this is Mr. Kamimura,\Nthe owner of the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212107,1213442}I'm so glad…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214609,1217279}The Polar Tear is safe,\Nthank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217279,1218530}Ah… don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219614,1222868}St. Tail, she…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:30.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225370,1230333}Well now, Hayase has been caught.\NWanna come live at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233503,1236673}Okay! One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239301,1241428}This is to celebrate our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241970,1244055}Let's be good friends!
